window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The third in a sexy romance series from the best-selling author of <i>Saxon</i> and <i>Toxic Girl</i>, about the bad boys of the Wind Dragons Motorcycle Club and the women who fall in love with them. </p> <p>Tracker is everything I've ever wanted. I see him. I've watched time change him. I've been patient, but he still hasn't noticed me. Not the way I want him to. The more time I spend with the MC, the more I understand. When you want something, you have to take it. You have to fight for it. And Tracker is more than worth fighting for.... </p>"; 
